    <block wx:else>
        <text class="title">Less than three steps learn how to use NPM</text>
        <view class="item">
            1.⁠ run <text class="code">npm init</text>⁠ in root project if this project has no package.json
        </view>
        <view class="item">
            2. run <text class="code">npm install sjcl</text> ⁠to create node_modules
        </view>
        <view class="item">
            3. do miniprogram npm compile menus -> Tool ->  Build npm
            <image class="guide-image" src="../../assets/guide.png" mode="aspectFit"/>
        </view>
        <view></view>
    </block>
</view>
